---
title: Dukkah-Spiced Bocconcini Wraps with Hummus and Pickled Onions
description: Bocconcini dusted with toasted spices and nuts are the star of this dish! But the supporting actors; DIY pickled onions, silky hummus and crisp salad, bring this dinner all together!
